{"rightSidebarLinks":[{"id":"dynamic","title":"dynamic","subLink":null},{"id":"basicview","title":"Basic View","subLink":[]},{"id":"customclassforsizing","title":"Custom Class For Sizing","subLink":[]},{"id":"readonlyplaintext","title":"Readonly Plain Text","subLink":[]},{"id":"disabledspecificcheckbox","title":"Disabled Specific Checkbox","subLink":[]},{"id":"disabledspecificradio","title":"Disabled Specific Radio","subLink":[]},{"id":"advancelayout","title":"Advance Layout","subLink":[]},{"id":"horizontalform","title":"Horizontal Form","subLink":[]},{"id":"horizontalformlabelsizing","title":"Horizontal Form Label Sizing","subLink":[]},{"id":"inlineform","title":"Inline Form","subLink":[]}],"title":"Power of Dynamic Forms","description":"rxweb dynamic forms is giving wide variety of features wich include horizontal forms, inline form, customized sizing for formControls, customized controls like plaintext mode for checkbox, radio and other formcontrols.","validatorType":"validators","validationTypeTitle":"Validators","type":"simple","category":"dynamic-forms","subCategory":"","linkTitle":"dynamic","tabArray":{},"innerHtml":null,"htmlContent":"<div class=\"title-bar\"><p>rxweb dynamic forms is giving wide variety of features including horizontal and inline form, customized sizing for formControls, customized controls like plaintext mode for checkbox, radio and other formcontrols.</p></div>\r\n<div class='row page-section' id= 'basicview'>\r\n<div class='col-lg-12'>\r\n<h2>Basic View<a title='Link to this heading' class='link-header' href='/reactive-dynamic-forms/dynamic-forms/dynamic#basicview'><i class='fa fa-link'></i></a></h2>\r\n\r\n<div component=\"app-example-runner\" ref-component=\"app-dynamic-basic\" title=\"Basic View\" key=\"basic\"></div>\r\n</div></div>\r\n<div class='row page-section' id= 'customclassforsizing'>\r\n<div class='col-lg-12'>\r\n<h2>Custom Class For Sizing<a title='Link to this heading' class='link-header' href='/reactive-dynamic-forms/dynamic-forms/dynamic#customclassforsizing'><i class='fa fa-link'></i></a></h2>\r\n\r\n<p class='showHideElement' >To apply customized sizing on formcontrols, you can use <span class='highlighted'>class</span> property to apply <span class='highlighted'>.form-control-lg</span> and <span class='highlighted'>.form-control-sm</span> bootstrap class.</p>\r\n<div component=\"app-example-runner\" ref-component=\"app-dynamic-customSizing\" title=\"Custom Class For Sizing\" key=\"customSizing\"></div>\r\n</div></div>\r\n<div class='row page-section' id= 'readonlyplaintext'>\r\n<div class='col-lg-12'>\r\n<h2>Readonly Plain Text<a title='Link to this heading' class='link-header' href='/reactive-dynamic-forms/dynamic-forms/dynamic#readonlyplaintext'><i class='fa fa-link'></i></a></h2>\r\n\r\n<p class='showHideElement' >To apply plaintext mode on any specific formControl, you can use <span class='highlighted'>isPlainTextMode</span> property of <span class='highlighted'>additionalconfig</span>.</p>\r\n<div component=\"app-example-runner\" ref-component=\"app-dynamic-plainText\" title=\"Readonly Plain Text\" key=\"plainText\"></div>\r\n</div></div>\r\n<div class='row page-section' id= 'disabledspecificcheckbox'>\r\n<div class='col-lg-12'>\r\n<h2>Disabled Specific Checkbox<a title='Link to this heading' class='link-header' href='/reactive-dynamic-forms/dynamic-forms/dynamic#disabledspecificcheckbox'><i class='fa fa-link'></i></a></h2>\r\n\r\n<p class='showHideElement' >To disable a specific checkbox in your dynamic form, you can pass <span class='highlighted'>disabled: true</span> to that checkbox in the server response.</p>\r\n<div component=\"app-example-runner\" ref-component=\"app-dynamic-disabledCheckbox\" title=\"Disabled Specific Checkbox\" key=\"disabledCheckbox\"></div>\r\n</div></div>\r\n<div class='row page-section' id= 'disabledspecificradio'>\r\n<div class='col-lg-12'>\r\n<h2>Disabled Specific Radio<a title='Link to this heading' class='link-header' href='/reactive-dynamic-forms/dynamic-forms/dynamic#disabledspecificradio'><i class='fa fa-link'></i></a></h2>\r\n\r\n<p class='showHideElement' >To disable a specific radio in your dynamic form, you can pass <span class='highlighted'>disabled: true</span> to that radio in server response.</p>\r\n<div component=\"app-example-runner\" ref-component=\"app-dynamic-disabledRadio\" title=\"Disabled Specific Radio Button\" key=\"disabledRadio\"></div>\r\n</div></div>\r\n<div class='row page-section' id= 'advancelayout'>\r\n<div class='col-lg-12'>\r\n<h2>Advance Layout<a title='Link to this heading' class='link-header' href='/reactive-dynamic-forms/dynamic-forms/dynamic#advancelayout'><i class='fa fa-link'></i></a></h2>\r\n\r\n<p class='showHideElement' >You can make your dynamically generated form in any of the customized or advance layout by using class and viewMode property .</p>\r\n<div component=\"app-example-runner\" ref-component=\"app-dynamic-advanceLayout\" title=\"Advance Layout\" key=\"advanceLayout\"></div>\r\n</div></div>\r\n<div class='row page-section' id= 'horizontalform'>\r\n<div class='col-lg-12'>\r\n<h2>Horizontal Form<a title='Link to this heading' class='link-header' href='/reactive-dynamic-forms/dynamic-forms/dynamic#horizontalform'><i class='fa fa-link'></i></a></h2>\r\n\r\n<p class='showHideElement' >To make a dynamic form  with horizontal layout, you need to pass <span class='highlighted'>viewMode=\"horizontal\"</span> and you can customize the horizontal form design by passing class name in viewMode property in server response.</p>\r\n<div component=\"app-example-runner\" ref-component=\"app-dynamic-horizontalLayout\" title=\"Horizontal Layout Form\" key=\"horizontalLayout\"></div>\r\n</div></div>\r\n<div class='row page-section' id= 'horizontalformlabelsizing'>\r\n<div class='col-lg-12'>\r\n<h2>Horizontal Form Label Sizing<a title='Link to this heading' class='link-header' href='/reactive-dynamic-forms/dynamic-forms/dynamic#horizontalformlabelsizing'><i class='fa fa-link'></i></a></h2>\r\n\r\n<p class='showHideElement' >You can also customize the label size of the horizontal dynamic form, by using <span class='highlighted'>viewMode</span> property in server response.</p>\r\n<div component=\"app-example-runner\" ref-component=\"app-dynamic-labelSizing\" title=\"Horizontal Form Label Sizing\" key=\"labelSizing\"></div>\r\n</div></div>\r\n<div class='row page-section' id= 'inlineform'>\r\n<div class='col-lg-12'>\r\n<h2>Inline Form<a title='Link to this heading' class='link-header' href='/reactive-dynamic-forms/dynamic-forms/dynamic#inlineform'><i class='fa fa-link'></i></a></h2>\r\n\r\n<p class='showHideElement' >You can also create inline forms through reactive-dynamic-forms and customize it through viewMode and class property.</p>\r\n<div component=\"app-example-runner\" ref-component=\"app-dynamic-inlineForm\" title=\"Inline Form\" key=\"inlineForm\"></div>\r\n</div></div>\r\n"}